article.headline: Bryant 23, Iona 7
article.story: NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y. -- Lindsey Gamble and Jerell Smith each rushed for more than 100 yards to help Bryant beat Iona 23-7 on Saturday. Gamble had 15 carries for 163 yards and a 75-yard touchdown run. Smith ran 15 times for 105 yards and two scores, the second from 50 yards out. Bryant (6-4) scored 23 straight points after Iona went up 7-0 on Warren Smith's 33-yard pass to Tim Mastrino. Iona (3-8) outgained Bryant 389-377, but had 136 yards in penalties. Warren Smith was 30-for-52 for 256 yards.
